00:13:18,647 --> 00:13:20,565
- 什麼遺言？ - 你沒看報紙嗎？
What were they? You don't read the papers.

148
00:13:20,649 --> 00:13:23,151
凱恩先生臨終時只留下了四個字
When Charles Foster Kane died, he said one word:

149
00:13:23,235 --> 00:13:24,236
 “玫瑰花蕾”
"Rosebud."

150
00:13:24,319 --> 00:13:26,071
- 他就說了這幾個字？
That's all he said? Tough guy.

151
00:13:26,154 --> 00:13:28,448
- 對，“玫瑰花蕾”，就這麼四個字！
Yes, "Rosebud." Just that one word.

152
00:13:28,782 --> 00:13:30,492
- 可是她是誰… - 或者是指什麼東西？
-But who is she? -What was it?

153
00:13:30,534 --> 00:13:32,703
這個人本有可能成為總統…
Here's a man who could've been president...

154
00:13:32,786 --> 00:13:35,080
象我們時代的每個人一樣 招人愛，招人恨，招人議論
...who was as loved, hated and talked about...

155
00:13:35,163 --> 00:13:37,708
但是當他死到臨頭時，掛念著的 卻是一個叫做玫瑰花蕾的什麼東西
...as any man in our time, but when he dies...

156
00:13:37,791 --> 00:13:40,043
但是當他死到臨頭時，掛念著的 卻是一個叫做玫瑰花蕾的什麼東西
...something is on his mind called Rosebud.

157
00:13:40,127 --> 00:13:42,587
- 這個詞兒意味著什麼？ - 也許是他曾經押過賭注的賽馬
-What does that mean? -A racehorse he bet on once.

158
00:13:42,671 --> 00:13:45,007
- 而且沒有中彩 - 好…是哪次賽馬？
-That didn't come in. -But what was the race?

159
00:13:45,090 --> 00:13:46,258
玫瑰花蕾
Rosebud.

160
00:13:46,341 --> 00:13:47,175
- 湯姆遜！ - 是的
-Thompson. -Yes.

161
00:13:47,217 --> 00:13:49,177
把片子留一兩個星期，如果有必要的話
Hold this up a week, two if you must.

162
00:13:49,219 --> 00:13:51,013
您不認為就在他剛死後立即發行 可能更好…
Don't you think right after he's dead--

163
00:13:51,096 --> 00:13:54,224
弄清楚玫瑰花蕾的來歷！ 去找每一個認識他的人…
Find out about Rosebud. Get in touch with anybody who knew him...

164
00:13:54,308 --> 00:13:55,809
…或瞭解他的人
...or knew him well.

165
00:13:56,143 --> 00:13:57,769
他的那個經理…
That manager of his....

166
00:13:57,853 --> 00:14:00,314
伯恩斯坦，他的第二個老婆 她還活著
Bernstein. His second wife. She's still living.

167
00:14:00,397 --> 00:14:01,690
蘇珊·亞歷山大·凱恩
Susan Alexander Kane.

168
00:14:01,732 --> 00:14:04,609
- 她在亞特蘭大城開一家夜總會 - 好的！
-She runs a nightclub in Atlantic City. -That's right.

169
00:14:04,693 --> 00:14:08,113
把他們全都訪問一遍，所有為他工作的人…
See them all. Get in touch with everybody that ever worked for him...

170
00:14:08,196 --> 00:14:11,074
…愛他的人，恨透了他的人
...whoever loved him, whoever hated his guts.

171
00:14:11,408 --> 00:14:14,411
我當然不是說要查遍姓名地址錄
I don't mean go through the city directory of course.

172
00:14:14,494 --> 00:14:16,079
我立即出發，若爾斯東先生
I'll get on it right away.

173
00:14:16,163 --> 00:14:18,874
好的！玫瑰花蕾，死活都要！
Good. Rosebud, dead or alive.

174
00:14:19,708 --> 00:14:22,294
也可能是一件很簡單的東西
It will probably turn out to be a very simple thing.

175
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:03,251
亞歷山大小姐
Miss Alexander.

176
00:15:04,461 --> 00:15:06,713
這位是湯姆遜先生，亞歷山大小姐
This is Mr. Thompson, Miss Alexander.

177
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:09,174
再來一杯，約翰
I want another drink, John.

178
00:15:12,094 --> 00:15:15,055
馬上就來，您要什麼嗎，湯姆遜先生？
Right away. Will you have something, Mr. Thompson?

179
00:15:15,097 --> 00:15:18,642
- 我想要一杯蘇打威士卡 - 誰讓你在這兒坐下來的？
-I'll have a highball, please. -Who told you you could sit down?

180
00:15:20,519 --> 00:15:22,437
我想也許我們可以一起喝一杯
I thought maybe we could have a talk.

181
00:15:22,521 --> 00:15:23,981
再想想！
Think again.

182
00:15:25,273 --> 00:15:27,567
為什麼你們總是纏著我？
Can't you people leave me alone?

183
00:15:27,651 --> 00:15:29,903
我不管別人的閒事，你們也別管我的
I'm minding my own business, you mind yours.

184
00:15:29,945 --> 00:15:32,906
我只想和您簡單地談談 亞歷山大小姐，我只是…
If I could just have a talk with you, Miss Alexander. I'd--

185
00:15:32,948 --> 00:15:34,491
滾出去！
Get out of here.

186
00:15:36,284 --> 00:15:37,536
滾！
Get out!

187
00:15:38,912 --> 00:15:40,414
- 抱歉 - 滾！
-Sorry. -Get out.

188
00:15:40,706 --> 00:15:43,166
- 能不能另找時間… - 滾！
-Maybe some other time. -Get out.

189
00:15:54,177 --> 00:15:55,304
金諾
Gino.

190
00:15:57,222 --> 00:15:58,974
再給她拿一杯蘇打威士卡
Get her another highball.

191
00:15:59,433 --> 00:16:01,977
她就是不願跟任何人說話，湯姆遜先生
She just won't talk to nobody, Mr. Thompson.

192
00:16:02,060 --> 00:16:03,145
沒關係
Okay.

193
00:16:05,272 --> 00:16:07,983
- 再要一杯雙料的？ - 對
-Another double? -Yeah.

194
00:16:08,942 --> 00:16:10,694
你好，我要紐約市
Hello, I want New York City.

195
00:16:10,777 --> 00:16:15,282
考特蘭7-9970 這堿O亞特蘭大城4-6827，好的
Courtland 79970. This is Atlantic City 46827. All right.

196
00:16:18,410 --> 00:16:19,953
她…
She's....

197
00:16:20,662 --> 00:16:22,289
她是借酒澆愁
She'll snap out of it.

198
00:16:22,456 --> 00:16:25,751
在凱恩先生去世以前 她隨時都願意談到他…
Why, until he died, she'd just as soon talk about Mr. Kane as any--

199
00:16:25,834 --> 00:16:27,210
- 哈羅 - 可現在…
-Hello. -Sooner.

200
00:16:27,336 --> 00:16:29,963
我是湯姆遜，我要和頭兒說話，好嗎？
This is Thompson. Let me talk to the chief.

201
00:16:31,757 --> 00:16:33,759
若爾斯東先生，她不願談
Mr. Rawlston? She won't talk.

202
00:16:34,009 --> 00:16:36,845
第二任凱恩太太 關於玫瑰花蕾或其他任何事！
The second Mrs. Kane. About Rosebud or anything else.

203
00:16:36,928 --> 00:16:38,680
我現在從亞特蘭大城打電話給你
I'm calling from Atlantic City.

204
00:16:38,764 --> 00:16:42,392
明天早上我就到費城去 到賽切爾的圖書館，看一下他的那本日記
Tomorrow I'll go to Philadelphia, to Thatcher Library, to see his diary.

205
00:16:42,476 --> 00:16:43,852
我跟他們約好了
They're expecting me.

206
00:16:43,894 --> 00:16:47,439
然後去紐約和凱恩的總經理見面 名字叫…伯恩斯坦
Then I've a meeting with his general manager in New York. Bernstein.

207
00:16:47,522 --> 00:16:49,024
之後我再返回此地
Then I'm coming back here.

208
00:16:49,066 --> 00:16:52,027
是的，所有還活著的我都去拜訪 再見，若爾斯東先生
Yeah, I'll see everybody that's still alive. Goodbye.

209
00:16:54,029 --> 00:16:54,988
- 嘿…呃… - 約翰
-Hey.... -John.

210
00:16:55,072 --> 00:16:56,907
約翰，你可能會幫上我的忙
You just might be able to help me.

211
00:16:56,990 --> 00:17:00,702
她過去談到凱恩的時候 有沒有提到過——玫瑰花蕾？
When she used to talk about Mr. Kane, did she ever mention Rosebud?

212
00:17:01,244 --> 00:17:02,579
“玫瑰花蕾”？
"Rosebud"?

213
00:17:02,954 --> 00:17:04,998
謝謝您，湯姆遜先生，謝謝
Thank you, Mr. Thompson, thanks.

214
00:17:05,499 --> 00:17:09,503
說老實話，就在前幾天 當報紙上報導了這件事的時候…
As a matter of fact, just the other day, when the papers were full of it...

215
00:17:10,962 --> 00:17:13,090
…我問過她
...l asked her.

216
00:17:13,632 --> 00:17:15,759
她從來沒有聽說過什麼玫瑰花蕾
She never heard of Rosebud.

217
00:17:27,938 --> 00:17:32,526
賽切爾紀念圖書館的負責人 要我再次提醒您…
The directors of the Thatcher Memorial Library have asked me to remind you...

218
00:17:32,693 --> 00:17:35,362
…只有在遵守約定的情況下你才能…
...about the conditions under which you may...

219
00:17:35,404 --> 00:17:38,573
…閱讀賽切爾先生未發表回憶錄的一部分
...inspect certain portions of Mr. Thatcher's unpublished memoirs.

220
00:17:38,657 --> 00:17:41,284
- 那沒問題 - 是的，詹尼斯，我現在就帶他進去
-l remember them. -Yes, Jennings, I'll bring him in.

221
00:17:41,368 --> 00:17:43,912
- 我只需要一個小時… - 決不允許…
-All I want is an hour-- -Under no circumstances...

222
00:17:43,996 --> 00:17:47,749
…直接引用他的手稿，跟我來
...are direct quotes from his manuscript to be used by you. You may follow me.

223
00:17:47,833 --> 00:17:50,043
好的，我只想尋找…
That's all right. I'm just looking for--

224
00:18:02,764 --> 00:18:04,391
詹尼斯
Jennings.

225
00:18:09,438 --> 00:18:10,897
謝謝你，詹尼斯
Thank you, Jennings.

226
00:18:11,565 --> 00:18:14,776
你必須在4點30分離開這個房間
You will be required to leave this room at 4:30 promptly.

227
00:18:15,110 --> 00:18:17,654
我們的協議是，你只能閱讀…
You will confine yourself, it is our understanding...

228
00:18:17,738 --> 00:18:21,241
…賽切爾手稿中有關凱恩先生的章節
...to the chapters in Mr. Thatcher's manuscript regarding Mr. Kane.

229
00:18:21,283 --> 00:18:23,201
我感興趣的就是這個
That's all I'm interested in.

230
00:18:24,119 --> 00:18:25,495
謝謝
Thank you.

231
00:18:26,788 --> 00:18:29,750
從83頁到142頁
Pages 83 to 142.

232
00:19:08,163 --> 00:19:09,956
快來啊
Come on, boys.

233
00:19:10,123 --> 00:19:11,458
小心，查理斯！
Be careful, Charles.

234
00:19:11,625 --> 00:19:12,459
凱恩太太
Mrs. Kane.

235
00:19:12,501 --> 00:19:14,711
把圍脖圍好，查理斯
Pull your muffler around your neck, Charles.

236
00:19:14,795 --> 00:19:17,047
凱恩太太，我們現在該告訴他了
Mrs. Kane, I think we'll have to tell him now.

237
00:19:17,130 --> 00:19:20,634
我現在就在這些契紙上簽字，賽切爾先生
Yes, I'll sign those papers now, Mr. Thatcher.

238
00:19:21,259 --> 00:19:24,096
看來你們這些人忘了我是孩子的父親
You people seem to forget that I'm the boy's father.

239
00:19:24,179 --> 00:19:27,099
一切完全按照我跟賽切爾先生說的辦
It's going to be done exactly the way I've told Mr. Thatcher.

240
00:19:27,182 --> 00:19:30,894
卡羅拉多沒什麼不好的 我不明白我們為什麼不能自己撫養孩子…
There's nothing wrong with Colorado. I don't see why we can't raise our son...

241
00:19:30,978 --> 00:19:32,771
…難道僅僅因為變得有錢？
...just 'cause we came into money.

242
00:19:32,854 --> 00:19:35,816
如果我願意的話，我可以告到法院去 當父親的有這樣的權利
If I want to, I can go to court. A father has a right to.

243
00:19:35,857 --> 00:19:39,194
一個房客交不起房租 留下了一張毫無價值的股票…
A boarder that beats his bill and leaves worthless stock behind....

244
00:19:39,236 --> 00:19:42,197
如果這張股票值錢了…
That property is as much my property as anybody's...

245
00:19:42,239 --> 00:19:45,200
…那它同樣也是我的財產 如果弗萊德·格雷夫料到…
...now that it's valuable. And if Fred Graves had any idea...

246
00:19:45,242 --> 00:19:48,829
…這樣的事，他本會在那些證件上 寫上我們兩人的名字了
...this would happen, he'd have made out the certificates in both our names.

247
00:19:48,912 --> 00:19:52,374
- 但是上面寫的是凱恩太太的名字 - 他欠的是我們兩人的膳宿費
-But they're made out to Mrs. Kane. -He owed the money to both of us.

248
00:19:52,457 --> 00:19:57,295
-“銀行關於所有事項的決定…” - 我不同意把我的孩子託付給銀行…
-"The bank's decision in all matters--" -l don't hold with giving Charles to a bank--

249
00:19:57,379 --> 00:19:59,631
- 我要求你別瞎鬧了，吉姆 - 我們文化程度不高…
-Stop this nonsense. -We're a bit uneducated--

250
00:19:59,715 --> 00:20:01,842
銀行關於教育方面的決定…
"The bank's decision concerning his education...

251
00:20:01,883 --> 00:20:04,386
“…比如他的居住地點，是最終的決定”
"...his places of residence, is to be final."

252
00:20:04,469 --> 00:20:08,015
- 一想到要讓銀行來當監護人… - 你就別瞎鬧了，吉姆
-The idea of a bank being the guardian-- -Stop this nonsense, Jim.

253
00:20:08,098 --> 00:20:11,018
“我們將接管科羅拉多的洛德礦井 的全部經營管理”…
"We will assume full management of the Colorado Lode"...

254
00:20:11,059 --> 00:20:13,729
…我重複一遍，凱恩太太， 您是唯一的產權所有人
...which I repeat, Mrs. Kane, you are the sole owner.

255
00:20:13,812 --> 00:20:15,981
- 簽在哪裡，賽切爾先生？ - 就在這堙A凱恩太太
-Where do I sign, Mr. Thatcher? -Right here.

256
00:20:16,064 --> 00:20:18,483
瑪麗，我最後一次請求你…
Mary, I'm asking you for the last time.

257
00:20:19,067 --> 00:20:21,737
大家都會認為我不是一個好丈夫或者父親
You'd think I hadn't been a good husband or father--

258
00:20:21,820 --> 00:20:23,363
你們兩位都在世的時候…
The sum of $50,000 a year...

259
00:20:23,447 --> 00:20:26,658
…每年將付給您和凱恩先生50,000元…
...is to be paid to you and Mr. Kane as long as you both live...

260
00:20:26,742 --> 00:20:28,869
…在此之後，則付給健在的人
...and thereafter to the survivor.

261
00:20:29,453 --> 00:20:32,372
- 好吧，但願一切如願 - 是這樣的
-Let's hope it's all for the best. -It is.

262
00:20:37,502 --> 00:20:40,839
我無法理解我為什麼不能撫養自己的孩子
Why I can't raise my own boy is more than I can understand.

263
00:20:40,922 --> 00:20:42,758
賽切爾先生，說下去
Go on, Mr. Thatcher.

264
00:20:42,883 --> 00:20:46,011
其他一切東西，資本和全部收益…
Everything else, the principal, as well as all monies earned...

265
00:20:46,094 --> 00:20:50,140
…均由銀行代您的兒子 查理斯·福斯特·凱恩管理
...is to be administered by the bank in trust for your son, Charles Foster Kane...

266
00:20:50,223 --> 00:20:52,976
…直到他二十五歲生日，屆時…
...until he reaches his 25th birthday, at which time...

267
00:20:53,060 --> 00:20:55,312
…將全都歸他所有
...he is to come into complete possession.

268
00:20:55,395 --> 00:20:56,688
查理斯！
Charles!

269
00:20:58,774 --> 00:21:00,359
說下去，賽切爾先生
Go on, Mr. Thatcher.

270
00:21:01,485 --> 00:21:05,113
快五點了，凱恩太太 你看我是不是該見見孩子？
It's almost 5:00. Don't you think I'd better meet the boy?

271
00:21:05,947 --> 00:21:07,908
我已經把他的箱子收拾好了
I've got his trunk all packed.

272
00:21:09,076 --> 00:21:11,244
幾個禮拜以前我就把它收拾好了
I've had it packed for a week now.

273
00:21:13,914 --> 00:21:16,291
我已經安排好，讓一位教師在芝加哥等我們
I've arranged for a tutor to meet us in Chicago.

274
00:21:16,333 --> 00:21:18,669
我本打算帶他一起來，但是…
I'd have brought him here with me, but....

275
00:21:19,419 --> 00:21:21,129
- 查理斯 - 嘿，媽媽
-Charles. -Look, Mom.

276
00:21:21,296 --> 00:21:22,756
你最好進屋來
You'd better come inside.

277
00:21:22,798 --> 00:21:25,801
- 雪人做得不錯  - 我把它嘴堛熒炾垣酗U來了
-That's quite a snowman. -l took the pipe out of his mouth.

278
00:21:25,842 --> 00:21:27,386
是你自己做的嗎？
Did you make it yourself?.

279
00:21:27,469 --> 00:21:30,013
或許我還可以做幾個牙和鬍鬚
Maybe I'll make some teeth and whiskers.

280
00:21:30,305 --> 00:21:32,349
這是賽切爾先生，查理斯
This is Mr. Thatcher, Charles.

281
00:21:32,766 --> 00:21:34,851
- 你好 - 你好，查理斯？
-Hello. -How do you do, Charles?

282
00:21:34,935 --> 00:21:36,478
他是從東部來的
He comes from the East.

283
00:21:36,561 --> 00:21:38,063
- 爸爸 - 哈羅，查理斯
-Pa. -Hello, Charlie.

284
00:21:38,146 --> 00:21:39,356
查理斯
Charles.

285
00:21:40,148 --> 00:21:41,483
什麼事，媽媽
Yes, Mommy.

286
00:21:43,068 --> 00:21:46,113
賽切爾先生今晚要帶你出遠門，查理斯
Mr. Thatcher is going to take you on a trip with him tonight.

287
00:21:46,196 --> 00:21:47,948
你要乘10次車走
You'll be leaving on number 10.

288
00:21:47,990 --> 00:21:50,200
就是那全點著燈的火車
That's the train with all the lights on it.

289
00:21:50,283 --> 00:21:51,284
你去嗎，媽媽？
You going, Mom?

290
00:21:51,368 --> 00:21:54,621
不，你母親不能馬上走，查理斯，但她會…
No. Your mother won't be going right away, but she'll....

291
00:21:55,330 --> 00:21:57,040
我上哪兒去？
Where am I going?

292
00:21:57,124 --> 00:22:00,919
你或許能去看看芝加哥、紐約和華盛頓 對嗎，柴契爾先生？
