-Mr. Bernstein, that's Mr. Leland, isn't it? -Yes, we're waiting for it.

1115
01:18:24,428 --> 01:18:27,514
- 他在哪？ - 就在那邊，凱恩先生
-Where is he? -Right in there, Mr. Kane.

1116
01:18:35,397 --> 01:18:36,898
凱恩先生
Mr. Kane.

1117
01:18:51,705 --> 01:18:54,374
李蘭先生和凱恩先生…
Mr. Leland and Mr. Kane...

1118
01:18:55,500 --> 01:18:58,754
已經有多年沒有說話了
...haven't spoken together for years.

1119
01:19:01,381 --> 01:19:04,051
- 你不是認為… - 沒什麼好認為的
-You don't suppose-- -There's nothing to suppose.

1120
01:19:08,430 --> 01:19:09,723
我去一下
Excuse me.

1121
01:19:26,782 --> 01:19:28,283
把門關上
Close the door.

1122
01:19:31,620 --> 01:19:34,164
他以前從未喝醉過
He ain't been drinking before.

1123
01:19:35,040 --> 01:19:37,125
從來沒有過，否則我們會聽說的
Never. We would have heard.

1124
01:19:37,459 --> 01:19:39,419
上面寫了些什麼？
What does it say there?

1125
01:19:39,920 --> 01:19:42,589
評論上面寫了些什麼？
The notice, what's he written?

1126
01:19:44,299 --> 01:19:49,262
蘇珊·亞歷山大小姐，一位漂亮的 但卻是毫無才華的業餘演員…
"Miss Susan Alexander, a pretty but hopelessly incompetent amateur...

1127
01:19:52,808 --> 01:19:56,645
昨晚在芝加哥新歌劇院的揭幕式上…
"...last night opened the new Chicago Opera House...

1128
01:19:56,979 --> 01:19:58,730
“演出…”
"...in a performance of...."

1129
01:20:01,817 --> 01:20:05,362
我還是讀不出那個劇名，凱恩先生
I still can't pronounce that name.

1130
01:20:08,865 --> 01:20:12,828
值得慶倖的是 她的歌唱不在本文論述範圍之內
"Her singing, happily, is no concern of this department.

1131
01:20:13,245 --> 01:20:17,165
“至於談到她的表演，那簡直無法…”
"Of her acting, it is absolutely impossible to...."

1132
01:20:18,875 --> 01:20:20,043
念下去！
Go on.

1133
01:20:22,504 --> 01:20:24,506
就這麼多
That's all there is.

1134
01:20:37,602 --> 01:20:41,148
至於談到她的表演，那簡直無法形容
Of her acting it is absolutely impossible to say anything except...

1135
01:20:41,231 --> 01:20:44,818
按照本文作者的意見 他達到了一個新的低點
...that, in the opinion of this reviewer, it represents a new low.

1136
01:20:45,027 --> 01:20:47,946
- 看見沒有，伯恩斯坦？按照本文意見… - 我沒有看見
-In the opinion of this reviewer. -l didn't see that.

1137
01:20:48,030 --> 01:20:50,365
上面沒有寫，伯恩斯坦先生，我在口述
It isn't here, Mr. Bernstein, I'm dictating it.

1138
01:20:50,449 --> 01:20:53,368
