-Hello. -Hello, Mr. Leland.

1142
01:21:27,986 --> 01:21:31,198
我的評論在哪，伯恩斯坦？ 我得把它寫完
Where's my notice, Bernstein? I've got to finish my notice.

1143
01:21:31,281 --> 01:21:34,534
- 凱恩先生在替你寫 - 查利？
-Mr. Kane is finishing it for you. -Charlie?

1144
01:21:40,540 --> 01:21:42,876
查利在那堙H
Charlie out there?

1145
01:21:44,628 --> 01:21:47,089
我猜他是在把它說圓了
I guess he's fixing it up.

1146
01:21:49,508 --> 01:21:51,927
我知道我編不出來
I knew I'd never get that through.

1147
01:21:52,761 --> 01:21:56,765
凱恩先生是按照你開始的觀點 來寫你的文章的
Mr. Kane's finishing your review just the way you started it.

1148
01:21:57,182 --> 01:22:00,894
他是用您用的那種嘲笑的口吻來寫的
He's writing a bad notice like you wanted it to be.

1149
01:22:03,397 --> 01:22:05,399
我想，這總該能向您徵明一點什麼吧
I guess that'll show you.

1150
01:22:30,299 --> 01:22:32,217
你好，傑德
Hello, Jedediah.

1151
01:22:35,470 --> 01:22:36,930
你好，查利
Hello, Charlie.

1152
01:22:38,515 --> 01:22:41,351
我不知道，我們倆該談談
I didn't know we were speaking.

1153
01:22:41,685 --> 01:22:43,937
當然，我們正在談著呢，傑德
Sure we're speaking, Jedediah.

1154
01:22:45,981 --> 01:22:48,150
你被解雇了
You're fired.

1155
01:23:00,454 --> 01:23:05,000
每個人都知道這件事，李蘭先生 但他為什麼要這麼做？
Everybody knows that story, Mr. Leland, but why did he do it?

