You may be right.

1344
01:41:07,749 --> 01:41:09,835
有時我也很困惑
I sometimes wonder...

1345
01:41:10,210 --> 01:41:12,629
但這已經成為習慣了
...but you get into the habit.

1346
01:41:12,713 --> 01:41:15,590
完全不是習慣，我玩這個是因為我喜歡它
It's not a habit, I do it because I like it.

1347
01:41:16,008 --> 01:41:18,593
