Invite everybody. Order everybody, you mean, and make them sleep in tents.

1350
01:41:28,729 --> 01:41:31,732
誰願意睡帳篷，他們都有自己的房間…
Who wants to sleep in tents when they've got their own room...

1351
01:41:31,773 --> 01:41:34,401
…和浴室，一切都很方便
...with a bath, where they know where everything is?

1352
01:41:34,484 --> 01:41:37,904
我想，明天我們可以去野餐
I thought we might have a picnic tomorrow.

1353
01:41:41,241 --> 01:41:45,579
我真正關心的事你都視而不見
You never give me anything I really care about.

1354
01:41:54,129 --> 01:41:56,006
這不是愛
"It can't be love

1355
01:41:58,508 --> 01:42:03,138
因為這堥S有真愛
"For there is no true love

1356
01:42:03,513 --> 01:42:06,016
我知道我在玩愛情遊戲
"l know I've played at the game

1357
