和它一樣，一無所得
"Lost in the end, just the same

1359
01:42:12,940 --> 01:42:15,442
這些年
"All these years

1360
01:42:15,609 --> 01:42:20,489
我含著淚水，心無定所
"My heart's been floating around in a puddle of tears

1361
01:42:22,908 --> 01:42:24,868
“我想知道這到底是什麼”
"l wonder what it is"

1362
