你只是買下你來為你作奉獻
You just tried to buy me into giving you something.

1373
01:43:02,698 --> 01:43:06,618
“這不是愛”
"It can't be love"

1374
01:43:19,464 --> 01:43:22,050
無論我做什麼，都是因為我愛你
Whatever I do, I do because I love you.

1375
01:43:22,134 --> 01:43:24,094
你不愛我
You don't love me.

1376
01:43:24,219 --> 01:43:26,179
你要我愛你
You want me to love you.

1377
01:43:26,221 --> 01:43:29,182
當然，我是查理斯·福斯特·凱恩
Sure. "I? Charles Foster Kane.

1378
01:43:29,224 --> 01:43:31,852
無論你要什麼，只要你說一聲好了
"Whatever you want, just name it and it's yours.

1379
01:43:31,935 --> 01:43:34,187
“但是你必須愛我”
"But you gotta love me."

1380
01:43:38,650 --> 01:43:41,361
不要說對不起
Don't tell me you're sorry.

1381
01:43:43,322 --> 01:43:45,073
我不會道歉的
I'm not sorry.

1382
01:43:56,918 --> 01:43:58,503
凱恩先生？
Mr. Kane?

1383
01:43:58,920 --> 01:44:01,673
凱恩夫人想見你
Mrs. Kane would like to see you, sir.

1384
01:44:04,551 --> 01:44:07,721
從一早起，梅莉就在收拾夫人的東西
Marie has been packing for her since morning.

1385
01:44:13,810 --> 01:44:17,522
梅莉，告訴阿爾諾德，我準備好了 告訴他可以來搬東西了
Tell Arnold I'm ready, Marie. Tell him he can get the bags.

1386
01:44:18,065 --> 01:44:19,316
好的，夫人
Yes, madame.

1387
01:44:21,318 --> 01:44:23,695
你真的瘋了嗎？
Have you gone completely crazy?

1388
01:44:23,779 --> 01:44:27,032
難道你不明白 我們的客人，每個人都知道這件事了嗎？
Don't you know that our guests, that everyone will know about this?

1389
01:44:27,115 --> 01:44:28,951
收拾好了東西，叫了汽車…
Packed your bag, sent for the car--

1390
01:44:29,034 --> 01:44:30,077
並且離開你？
And left you?

1391
01:44:30,369 --> 01:44:32,287
他們當然會知道的
Of course they'll hear.

1392
01:44:33,288 --> 01:44:35,958
除了你，我不和別人說再見
I'm not saying goodbye, except to you.

1393
01:44:36,166 --> 01:44:39,002
