Please don't go.

1398
01:45:14,746 --> 01:45:16,540
求求你，蘇珊
Please, Susan.

1399
01:45:19,751 --> 01:45:23,213
從現在開始，一切都按照你的意思辦
From now on, everything will be exactly the way you want it to be.

1400
01:45:23,297 --> 01:45:25,424
不是我所認為的你的意思，而是…
Not the way I think you want it, but...

1401
01:45:27,092 --> 01:45:28,593
