...your way.

1402
01:45:35,100 --> 01:45:36,435
你不能走
You mustn't go.

1403
01:45:39,688 --> 01:45:41,815
你不能這樣對我
You can't do this to me.

1404
01:45:43,525 --> 01:45:45,193
我明白了
I see.

1405
01:45:46,111 --> 01:45:48,655
又是只有你！
It's you that this is being done to.

1406
01:45:48,989 --> 01:45:50,782
我不算什麼
It's not me at all.

1407
01:45:51,033 --> 01:45:52,951
對我意味著什麼，也不重要
Not what it means to me.

1408
01:45:55,120 --> 01:45:57,289
我不能這樣對待你？
I can't do this to you?

1409
01:45:58,749 --> 01:46:00,709
噢，不，我能這樣
Oh, yes, I can.

1410
01:46:19,853 --> 01:46:22,981
也許您聽說過，我失去了所有的金錢 真的是很多的錢
In case you haven't heard, I lost all my money and it was plenty.

1411
01:46:23,065 --> 01:46:25,359
最近十年，很多人都很困難
The last 10 years have been difficult for many.

1412
01:46:25,442 --> 01:46:28,403
我並不困難，我只不過是喪失了金錢
They haven't been tough on me. I just lost all my money.

1413
01:46:29,029 --> 01:46:32,199
- 您要到上都莊園去嗎？ - 星期一，和編輯部的幾個同事一起去
-You're going down to Xanadu? -Monday, with boys from the office.

1414
01:46:32,240 --> 01:46:35,035
若爾斯東先生讓我們把整個莊園都拍下來
Mr. Rawlston wants the whole place photographed.

1415
01:46:35,077 --> 01:46:36,703
我們要出一個新聞片專輯
We run a picture magazine.

1416
01:46:36,745 --> 01:46:40,499
如果你夠聰明，就該去找雷蒙，他是管家
If you're smart, you'll get in touch with Raymond. He's the butler.

1417
01:46:40,582 --> 01:46:42,542
從他那兒您會瞭解很多事
You'll learn a lot from him.

1418
01:46:42,626 --> 01:46:45,128
別人不知道的，他都知道
He knows where all the bodies are buried.

1419
01:46:45,295 --> 01:46:48,507
您知道嗎，我總是為凱恩先生感到惋惜
You know, all the same, I feel kind of sorry for Mr. Kane.

1420
01:46:50,759 --> 01:46:52,427
您以為我就不為他惋惜嗎？
Don't you think I do?

1421
01:46:57,015 --> 01:46:59,977
您從我這瞭解些什麼呢？…已經是早上了
What do you know, it's morning already.

1422
01:47:03,438 --> 01:47:07,067
