How much is it worth to you?

1426
01:47:23,375 --> 01:47:25,168
-1000塊？
$1,000?

1427
01:47:34,469 --> 01:47:37,180
好吧，我告訴你，湯姆森先生
Well, I'll tell you, Mr. Thompson.

1428
01:47:37,889 --> 01:47:41,310
- 你知道嗎？他有時做事很可笑 - 不，我不知道
-He acted funny sometimes, you know? -No, I didn't.

1429
01:47:41,560 --> 01:47:43,979
