Yes, he did crazy things sometimes.

1430
01:47:44,313 --> 01:47:46,732
我在他這兒幹了十一年…
I've been working for him 11 years now...

1431
01:47:46,815 --> 01:47:50,611
管理整個莊園，我應該知道
...in charge of the whole place, so I ought to know.

1432
01:47:50,986 --> 01:47:52,279
- 玫瑰花蕾 - 是的
-Rosebud. -Yes.

1433
01:47:52,321 --> 01:47:57,326
正如我說的，他有時候很古怪…
Like I tell you, the old man acted kind of funny sometimes...

1434
01:47:57,409 --> 01:48:01,121
