Like that time his wife left.

1437
01:50:21,803 --> 01:50:23,055
玫瑰花蕾
Rosebud.

1438
01:51:31,123 --> 01:51:32,666
我知道了
I see.

1439
01:51:33,333 --> 01:51:35,794
