He just said:

1442
01:51:42,676 --> 01:51:44,511
“玫瑰花蕾”
"Rosebud."

1443
01:51:44,553 --> 01:51:47,848
那個玻璃球就從手中掉了下去，摔碎了
Then he dropped the glass ball and it broke on the floor.

1444
01:51:48,557 --> 01:51:52,769
之後凱恩先生就再也不說話了 於是我知道他已經死了
He didn't say anything after that, and I knew he was dead.

1445
01:51:53,520 --> 01:51:56,231
