He said all kinds of things that didn't mean anything.

1446
01:51:56,315 --> 01:51:58,317
您就沒有一點傷感嗎？
Sentimental fellow, aren't you?

1447
01:51:59,401 --> 01:52:02,070
- 也有，也沒有 - 這些不值1000元
-Yes and no. -That isn't worth $1,000.

1448
01:52:02,154 --> 01:52:05,157
如果您願意，可以向我提問題
You can keep on asking questions if you want to.

1449
01:52:05,407 --> 01:52:07,075
今天晚上就走…
We're leaving tonight...

1450
01:52:07,868 --> 01:52:09,828
等他們把宮殿拍完我們就走
...when we're through taking pictures.

1451
01:52:09,911 --> 01:52:11,872
多留點時間給自己
Allow yourself plenty of time.

1452
01:52:11,913 --> 01:52:15,792
火車根據信號停站 但他們不喜歡等人
The train stops at the junction on signal, but they don't like to wait.

1453
01:52:16,835 --> 01:52:19,796
九千一百八十二號
I can remember when they'd wait all day...

1454
01:52:20,130 --> 01:52:21,840
可我記得，他們曾等人等了一天…
...if Mr. Kane said so.

1455
01:52:23,258 --> 01:52:25,844
如果凱恩先生讓他們等
Better get going.

1456
01:52:28,847 --> 01:52:32,768
