How much do you think this is all worth, Mr. Thompson?

1458
01:52:38,649 --> 01:52:40,192
好幾百萬吧
Millions.

1459
01:52:41,652 --> 01:52:42,861
如果有人需要的話
If anybody wants it.

1460
01:52:42,945 --> 01:52:45,614
