-What's that? -Another Venus.

1462
01:52:47,532 --> 01:52:48,867
價值25000元
$25,000.

1463
01:52:48,951 --> 01:52:51,536
花這麼多錢買一個無頭的東西
A lot of money to pay for a dame without a head.

1464
01:52:51,620 --> 01:52:53,789
銀行太倒楣了？
The banks are out of luck?

1465
01:52:55,290 --> 01:52:58,043
- 他們都是即時結清的 - 他從來不扔東西
-They'll clear all right. -He never threw anything away.

1466
01:52:58,126 --> 01:53:03,298
